## 2. Scope
### 2.1 In Scope
- NextAuth-based auth integration (per architecture rules).
- Email/password registration + login.
- Social login: Google OAuth, Apple Sign In.
- Email verification flow.
- Password reset flow.
- Age verification gate via third-party provider.
- Basic account state handling: active, email-unverified, age-pending, age-denied, locked/suspended (state labels TBD by backend/tech lead).

### 2.2 Out of Scope
- MFA/2FA and phone/SMS OTP.
- Creator KYC (separate process).
- Admin tooling for manual review.
- Mobile app UX specifics.
- Payment or payout KYC.

