## 9. Risks & Mitigations
| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Email deliverability issues | Users blocked from verifying/resetting | Verify SPF/DKIM, monitor bounce, fallback resend |
| Vendor age check false negatives | Legit users blocked | Provide retry/appeal path; allow manual review later |
| Social login duplicate accounts | Fragmented identities | Clear linking rules; match on verified email |
| Apple private relay loss | Lost access when relay revoked | Encourage adding primary email post-signup |

